features.name: TPR_16,TPR_19 Exports the biofilm adhesin polysaccharide poly-beta- 1,6-N-acetyl-D-glucosamine (PGA) across the outer membrane. The PGA transported seems to be partially N-deacetylated since N- deacetylation of PGA by PgaB is needed for PGA export through the PgaA porin
- Evidence 5 No homology to any previously reported sequences
